{"type": "article", "id": 23930, "title": "Normann Copenhagen置物盒系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-16T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110243TIp05SKahZs1WVnF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套置物盒系列来自设计师，也是丹麦设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 的 2016 新品。它有 5 种型号和 7 种颜色选择，想让所有零碎物品都能放进来并搭配地好看。铁制盒子或盘子的四面都有圆孔，细看时会发现圆孔呈现椭圆和圆形间隔排列，让人在视觉上看起来舒服。售价 26 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/search?q=Nic%20Nac\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110242paRFv7PCVg4IY5zc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.74166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110242znqmIliaBgrSdYFK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110242zl1rjgwHn6vXGCMJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110243lZtr7BpL8T0CeOWj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}